  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Piz Buin is in an excellent location in the heart of Klosters and only 2 minutes’ walk from the Gotschna cable-car. It has a cosy Alpine-style throughout and provides a luxurious and comfortable base from which to enjoy this fantastic ski area. The beautifully furnished interior is complemented by the high levels of service and cuisine, and its friendly atmosphere.</p>]]></description>
