  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>The spacious and attractively furnished twin ‘Classic’ rooms all face the village and have balcony, bath or shower, TV with English channels, telephone, radio, minibar, hairdryer, bathrobes, slippers and tea/coffee-making facilities.</li>
<li>‘Classic’ and ‘Alpenchic’ studios are larger and also have kitchenette, balcony and face the village or river.</li>
<li>‘Alpenchic’ studios are recently-renovated.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
